Further, the invention relates to the following aspects:
(2) an atropisomer according to (1), which is
(-)-1-(2-hydroxyethyl)-4-methyl-N-[4-(methylsulfonyl)phenyl]-5-[2-(trifluoromethyl)phenyl]-1H-pyrrole-3-carboxamide;
(3) an atropisomer according to (1), which is
(+)-1,4-dimethyl-N-[4-(methy-sulfonyl)phenyl]-5-[2-(trifluoromethyl)phenyl]-1H-pyrrole-3-carboxamide;
(4) an atropisomer according to (1)which is
(-)-1-(2-hydroxyethyl)-5-[4-methoxy-2-(trifluoromethyl)phenyl]-4-methyl-N-[4-(methylsulfonyl)phenyl]-1H-pyrrole-3-carboxamide;
(5) a pharmaceutical containing the atropisomer according to any one of (1) to (4) as an active ingredient;
(6) a prophylactic or therapeutic agent for a cardiovascular disease, containing the atropisomer according to any one of (1) to (4) as an active ingredient;
(7) a prophylactic or therapeutic agent for hypertension, containing the atropisomer according to any one of (1) to (4) as an active ingredient;
(8) a pharmaceutical composition comprising the atropisomer according to any one of (1) to (4) and a pharmacologically acceptable carrier.
